messages.messageBody:
Re: Intro and toothpaste question Hello!

Just wanted to introduce myself quickly and ask a rather off the wall question. I'm Amy, 24, SAHM to Accalia Grace, 17 months, and dw to Cory, 28, a mental health counselor at a juvenile training school. We all live in South Dakota.

I'm hoping somebody can help me with this. I thought of all people, this group might know. I have a few friends with toddlers who have tooth decay problems. I recall hearing a long time ago about some sort of black walnut toothpaste that did wonders for tooth decay. Does this ring a bell with anyone?

TIA.

Amy
Mama to Accalia (6/14/99)
"The hardest to learn was the least complicated" -Indigo Girls
